      "review_summary": "The PR changes two Feishu bot dispatcher call sites to pass computed `feishuTo` as the dispatcher `chatId` for p2p DM reply delivery.\n\nPR surface: Source 0. Total 0 across 1 file.\n\nReproducibility: yes. source-reproducible. Current main computes `user:<open_id>` for Feishu DMs, suppresses non-thread DM reply metadata, and still builds the dispatcher from raw `ctx.chatId`, matching the linked `replies=1` delivery failure.",
